{
  "article_id": "LosAngelesHerald1898",
  "paragraphs": [
    [
      {
        "text": "Slowly and before its time the island is being depopulated. Yesterday a crowd came over on"
      },
      {
        "text": "the steamer",
        "entity_key": "sh_steamer2",
        "entity_type": "ship"
      },
      {
        "text": "at 1 oclock, but returned at 3 oclock. September is the most delightful month here, but habit and school terms are unreasoning tyrants."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "Capt. \"Sandy\" McDonald",
        "entity_key": "smc",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "is telling the boys about a wonderful dog that he rescued last week, who had managed to follow his mistress from"
      },
      {
        "text": "Long Beach",
        "entity_key": "ci_lb",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "to the isthmus after she had left him on the"
      },
      {
        "text": "mainland",
        "entity_key": "re_mld",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ", disconsolate and alone."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "Herbert Gregg",
        "entity_key": "hgr",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "entertained Misses"
      },
      {
        "text": "Gertrude",
        "entity_key": "gmccrea",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "Mae McCrea",
        "entity_key": "mmc",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ","
      },
      {
        "text": "Frances",
        "entity_key": "fgr",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ","
      },
      {
        "text": "Dorothy",
        "entity_key": "dgr",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "Alice Groff",
        "entity_key": "agr",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "Edith Furrey",
        "entity_key": "efu",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ", Messrs."
      },
      {
        "text": "Burnham",
        "entity_key": "bpo",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "Harry Polley",
        "entity_key": "hpo",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "at a candy pull Saturday afternoon."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "Mr. Duyckinck",
        "entity_key": "duy",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ", who holds the record for the number of fish caught this season on rod and reel, is now bending all his efforts to catch the thirty-three fish necessary to make his total 1000 fish. Saturday he was out with"
      },
      {
        "text": "Mexican Joe",
        "entity_key": "mjoe",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and caught fifteen yellowtail. The fish were found at the isthmus and in great numbers, but the limited time that he had to spend there did not allow him to get any more fish."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "The church on the hill",
        "entity_key": "church",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "is to be enlarged during the winter. The additional room will be fitted out and used as a meeting and club room for those who stay here all winter. Magazines will be on the tables. Over $550 has been raised for the purpose."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "Dr. C. W. Bryson",
        "entity_key": "cbr",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "J. Todd Cook",
        "entity_key": "jco",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "secured seven goat heads the other day."
      },
      {
        "text": "N. Howard",
        "entity_key": "nho",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ","
      },
      {
        "text": "Mr.",
        "entity_key": "lcr",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "Mrs. L. C. Craig",
        "entity_key": "mlcr",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "H. M. Corlett",
        "entity_key": "hco",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "also secured four fine heads."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "The yacht"
      },
      {
        "text": "San Diego",
        "entity_key": "sh_sandiego",
        "entity_type": "ship"
      },
      {
        "text": "returned from"
      },
      {
        "text": "San Pedro",
        "entity_key": "ci_sp",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "yesterday. This afternoon the"
      },
      {
        "text": "San Diego",
        "entity_key": "sh_sandiego",
        "entity_type": "ship"
      },
      {
        "text": "will leave on an exploration trip to"
      },
      {
        "text": "San Nicolas",
        "entity_key": "i_sn",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ". A search will be made for the"
      },
      {
        "text": "Cave of the Lost Woman",
        "entity_key": "re_lwcave",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ", who was marooned on"
      },
      {
        "text": "the island",
        "entity_key": "i_sn",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "years ago. The party will consist of"
      },
      {
        "text": "E. L. Doran",
        "entity_key": "edo",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ","
      },
      {
        "text": "Sid Smith",
        "entity_key": "ssm",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "C. F. Holder",
        "entity_key": "cho",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "The"
      },
      {
        "text": "Hotel Pasadena",
        "entity_key": "hotelpasadena",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "has closed for the season."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "Miss Craig",
        "entity_key": "mcr",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "of"
      },
      {
        "text": "Pasadena",
        "entity_key": "ci_pa",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "is the guest of"
      },
      {
